Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.73,0:00:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是讓我們先去的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打個電話給她
