Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  我們先去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.48,0:00:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.75,0:01:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
