Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.73,0:01:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早起來彈了下吉太就變成這樣了…
