Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿了送給畢業生的花後就去大禮堂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到畢業典禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  要和學姐們說再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太好重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是輕音社  總是掙扎在死亡線上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  撞到了～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.36,0:04:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  平澤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  破了個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  早上來的時候摔了一跤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂把替換的緊身褲放在我這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  超能力者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去換掉
