Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是手忙腳亂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個你們還沒寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫給山中老師的留言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剩下小律你們的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在畢業典禮的日子發生這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  有劉海遮著看不見的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  畢業典禮能順利結束就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  沒事的  已經沒什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就請在校生為畢業生戴上花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:18.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快讓她們給你們戴花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  寫一下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送給小佐和的驚喜禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全班同學的留言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶來了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  無意中就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田井中同學  你們快到裡面去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個在典禮中要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當扇子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  在畢業典禮中不需要那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給小佐和保管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直這樣拿著怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在典禮中一直都這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:07:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  好像大禮堂和平時感覺不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是畢業典禮…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就開始第85屆櫻丘女子高級中學的畢業典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請校長致詞  起立
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…各位畢業生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有各位家長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是恭喜你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業生的各位在這三年間有很多的相識  也發生了很多故事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:39.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定產生了很多美好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太在意了  無法集中精神聽校長講話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們教職全員都從心底祝福大家今後表現活躍以及身體健康
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很在意唯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  起立
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是肚子疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.73,0:08:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  剛才隱藏了什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼？  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零食？  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉他？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是小豬？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,授予畢業證書
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各班代表請上台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意著唯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常在意的樣子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業生起立
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我傳話給唯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說佐和子老師很在意你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴唯是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田井中同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪的傳話  佐和子老師失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和失敗？  什麼失敗？  為什麼傳這話給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:48.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪想向我傳達什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業生答詞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到和和發言了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答詞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝大家今天為我們的畢業典禮而相聚到場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回首往事  在這所學校度過的三年非常充實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才典禮時太讓人在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也非常在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  小佐和失敗是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我說的是佐和子老師在擔心你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我這裡的時候還是擔心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  別管啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是你出的亂子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯寫好了嗎  紙箋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要抓緊時間寫咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你筆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小佐和  祝你幸福」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不太對吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚的話倒還可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都寫上去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這話很打擊吧  很打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那修正一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們先回一趟教室啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要發畢業證書給你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業典禮的時候你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在意得都不能集中精神參加典禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在保一樣東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下你就懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就告訴我  現在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回教室吧  佐和子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:30.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}畢業證書\N平澤唯\N十一月二十七日  生\N右方人士已經修完本校的高級中學課程\N特此證書\N櫻丘女子高級中學\N校長  沖山陽二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯也畢業了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托您的福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的畢業證書都沒發錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認過後妥善保管帶回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好喜歡這個聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的高中生活到此也就告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:10:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是我首個擔任班主任的班級
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常欣慰看到大家精神飽滿地迎來這一天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也多保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…解散
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有份謝禮要送給老師您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在誰手裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小唯  就拜託你贈送了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是返還優勝旗用的曲子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:43.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（運動會開幕式用的音樂，多用於甲子園）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山中老師  謝謝您的栽培
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說典禮上你拿的就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:03.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:05.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次做班主任遇到你們實在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空要記得回來玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老娘等著你們呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…喲  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:30.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和  好酷！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…純
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去爵士研活動室了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己多注意點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓也要去音樂室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人要為姐姐慶賀畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去準備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶賀…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶賀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說不能和姐姐穿同樣的制服有點遺憾…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過姐姐每次都走在我前面一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐嘛  也是沒辦法的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我也會好好祝賀的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能和輕音社一起…拍一張照嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  正中間正中間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要上同一所大學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也請繼續搞音樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園祭的時候…真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是帥氣或者好聽之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業旅行去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和真受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會不知道還來不來活動室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會來蹭茶喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去下學生會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見  和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再會了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後電話聯繫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:59.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（祝賀你們畢業）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:00.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（最喜歡山中老師  圭子）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這叫人怎麼擦嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想今天我來倒茶的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓  這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊  小梓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於今後…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們一直也沒怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力拉新人進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對  絕對  絕對不會廢社的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來我之前一直沒有好好向學姐們道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我寫了感謝信…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是剛剛才寫好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:15:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  現在能讀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？啊  好的  請隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都寫了些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  小梓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:25.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐們才是  恭喜你們畢業…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要畢業…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不整理活動室或者整天喝茶我也不責怪你們了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要畢業…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,額頭怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  明明是畢業典禮…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明該祝賀的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有帶著創可貼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來打算不哭的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要笑著送別的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會好好繼承輕音社…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…小豬也在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們一年級時候的照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比現在的梓喵還要年輕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這個也送給你  五枚花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們很像呢  梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝什麼酷嘛  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就唯一個人太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓  有首歌希望你能聽一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  連澪也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為梓喵創作的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  這是我的台詞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========================
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:39.07,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天使にふれたよ」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:47.85,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ　思い出のカケラに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:54.20,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名前をつけて保存するなら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:58.07,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「宝物」がピッタリだね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:08.49,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう　心の容量が　いっぱいになるくらいに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:14.40,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過ごしたね　トキメキ色の毎日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:19.52,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なじんだ　制服と上ばき
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:23.77,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ホワイトボードの落書き
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:27.84,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日の入り口に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:32.15,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おいてかなくちゃ　いけないのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:40.01,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でもね会えたよ　すてきな天使に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:44.06,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卒業は終わりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:48.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これからも　仲間だから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:56.45,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一緒の写真達　おそろのキーホルダー
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:20:00.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつまでも輝いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:06.68,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっと　その笑顔　ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:12.39,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駅のホーム　河原の道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:19.08,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離れてても　同じ空見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:25.68,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ユニゾンで歌おー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:37.49,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でもね　会えたよ　素敵な天使に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:41.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卒業は終わりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:45.84,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これからも　仲間だから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:53.87,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大好きって言うなら　大大好きって返すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:57.83,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れ物　もうないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:21:04.24,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっと永遠に　一緒だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:39.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「相遇天使」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:47.85,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果回憶的碎片　
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:54.20,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取個名字來保存
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:58.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就應該是「寶物」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:08.49,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯　無比充實地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:14.40,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,度過繽紛的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:19.52,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熟悉的校服和拖鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:23.77,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有白板上的塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:27.84,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在明天的入口處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:32.15,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須全部留下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:40.01,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是　相遇了　美麗的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:44.06,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業不會是終點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:48.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:56.45,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一同擁有的照片　一起持有的掛墜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:20:00.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時都那麼閃爍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:06.68,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這永遠的笑容　道聲謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:12.39,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車站的站台　河岸的走道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:19.08,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使相隔遙遠　遙望同一天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:25.68,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同聲齊唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:37.49,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是　相遇了　美麗的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:41.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業不會是終點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:45.84,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:53.87,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那聲「最喜歡」　換回「最最喜歡」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:57.83,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有遺憾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:21:04.24,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們永遠會在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========================
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很精彩呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還想再繼續聽下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接著梓喵也一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.39,0:21:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  能聽一下我們的曲子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}終
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.90,0:23:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}她們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.26,0:23:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  輕音社是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.09,0:23:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三樓的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.45,0:23:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別考慮得太複雜比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.47,0:23:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊  總之先把想到的東西隨便寫出來放在一起看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.31,0:23:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三樓？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.32,0:23:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒怎麼聽到過練習的聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.25,0:23:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視頻就用宣傳短片風格
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:24:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海邊倉庫之類的地方演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.12,0:24:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面用攝影機帥氣地拍下來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.74,0:24:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
